name: NFT BITSPACE
description: The history of Bitcoin begins in 2007-2008. Almost an irony, the world's first major virtual currency takes its first steps around the same time as the lehman brothers crash and one of the biggest financial crises in history. The fact is that in 2007 Satoshi Nakamoto began to develop the concept of Bitcoin (rumors gave account that the name designates a group, not a specific person). Hitoria index 1. The first transactions 2. Growth and evolution of Bitcoin's history 3. Not everything is flowers
